data.description: This immaculate 4-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom residence sits on a corner lot within the tranquil and sought-after neighborhood of Braunridge. Upon entry, a grand two-story foyer welcomes you into a freshly painted, thoughtfully designed open floor plan featuring lofty ceilings, elegant architectural arches, and newly installed carpeting throughout. The chef's kitchen is equipped with granite countertops, rich stained cabinets, and a central island, while the adjacent breakfast area offers serene views and access to a private covered patio. Tucked away beyond the kitchen is the secluded primary bedroom, boasting custom built-in shelves and a luxurious spa-like en-suite bathroom, complete with dual vanity sinks, a soaking tub, a separate shower, and a spacious walk-in closet. Upstairs, three generously sized bedrooms await, each boasting its own walk-in closet. Additional highlights of this home include an expansive two-car garage and a fully fenced backyard. Residents will appreciate the convenience of easy access to 1604 and IH10, as well as proximity to top-rated NISD schools and a wealth of other amenities.
